room_title: Escape room "Escape Area 51" by Race to Escape in Tampa
room_address: 2435 US Highway 19 N Suite 101 Holiday, FL 34691
room_description: You were on a peaceful tour of Area 51 until alarms began to blare. Quickly you were rushed to a room and locked in. You can hear chaos from outside the room. The military has been overrun by a group of extraterrestrials. You have to fly one of the extraterrestrials that died in your arms back to his mothership to convince their kind not to invade and destroy all humanity.
